%% state_04_task_assignment.mmd — TaskAssignment Status
%% Ref: task_assignment model (assignment_status: active/completed/cancelled)
%% Completed ALWAYS triggers ReviewSession creation

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> active : Assignment created\n(via approve application\nor manual assign)

    active --> completed : Task enters DONE category\n→ auto-mark completed\n→ ALWAYS create ReviewSession
    active --> cancelled : Task cancelled or\nassignment revoked

    completed --> [*]
    cancelled --> [*]

    note right of active
        assigned_at = auto-set on creation.
        estimated_hours, actual_hours tracked.
        hourly_rate for freelancer contracts.
    end note

    note right of completed
        completed ALWAYS triggers review:
        1. Create ReviewSession (status=pending)
        2. Set deadline = NOW() + 14 days
        3. Notify manager + peers
        4. Review is MANDATORY, not optional
    end note
